Site structure:
Navbar(on all pages):
  - logo
      - navigates to index
  - menu when not logged in
      - Log in
      - Register
      - Main page
  -menu when logged in:
      - Main page
      - Upload
      - Admin page
      - Log out
      - Display "Hi [user]!"
      
Index page:
  - navbar
  - list of article previews
      - clickable title
      - thumbnail
      - author
      - date
      - 350 character long preview text
      
Admin page:
  - like index
  - edit button
  - delete button
  
Upload page:
  - navbar
  - textbox for title
  - textarea for article
  - browse button for file upload
 
Edit page:
  - navbar
  - textbox for title
  - textarea for article
  - browse button for file upload
  - previously typed things displayed
 
Article page:
  - navbar
  - title
  - author
  - date
  - full content
  - back to top button
  - back to main page button
